Whoa, it's all right.

322
00:36:54,010 --> 00:36:56,520
- What?!
- I got to tell you, congratulations!

323
00:36:56,730 --> 00:37:00,520
It's okay if I get a picture
of you and your men?

324
00:37:00,730 --> 00:37:03,610
Yeah. But not for publication.
Just for us!

325
00:37:03,820 --> 00:37:06,440
Anything you say, Mr Ness.

326
00:37:06,650 --> 00:37:10,700
Closer in... Oh, that's great.
Okay, ready? Hold it.

327
00:37:18,410 --> 00:37:21,000
Life goes on.

328
