341
00:38:20,730 --> 00:38:23,100
Part of a team.

342
00:38:23,850 --> 00:38:26,570
Teamwork...

343
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:34,990
Looks, throws, catches, hustles.
Part of one big team.

344
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:41,410
Bats himself the live-long day,
Babe Ruth, Ty Cobb, and so on.

345
00:38:43,170 --> 00:38:47,210
If his team don't field...what is he?

346
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:51,300
You follow me?

347
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:54,220
No one.

348
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:59,510
Sunny day, the stands are full
of fans. What does he have to say?

349
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:05,150
I'm goin' out there for myself.

350
00:39:05,350 --> 00:39:11,860
But...I get nowhere
unless the team wins.

351
00:39:12,070 --> 00:39:14,360
- Team!
- Team.

