377
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:42,300
But we can get him on
income tax evasion if we can show

378
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:46,640
that any of the 'organisation'
business money is going to him.

379
00:41:46,850 --> 00:41:51,060
- Legally, he receives no income.
- He doesn't receive anything?

380
00:41:51,270 --> 00:41:54,820
- Mr Ness? You have a visitor.
- Mister Ness!

381
00:41:55,020 --> 00:41:58,110
Could we talk for a minute?
I'm John O'Shea, Alderman...

382
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:00,200
Yes, I know who you are.

383
00:42:03,120 --> 00:42:05,830
Would you excuse us?

384
00:42:07,830 --> 00:42:11,750
We are busy with several large
operations. What can I do for you?

385
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:15,170
I came up to congratulate you
on a job well done.

386
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:21,130
Share your good fortune
on such a lovely day.

387
00:42:24,930 --> 00:42:26,560
What's that?

388
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:34,520
- What is that?
- Mr Ness, you're an educated man.

389
00:42:34,730 --> 00:42:38,190
Let me pay you the compliment
of being blunt.

390
00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:44,200
There is a large and popular business
which you are causing dismay.

391
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:50,040
Why don't you just cross the street
and let things take their course?

392
00:42:50,250 --> 00:42:53,250
Would you come in here, please?

393
