Take it easy.

463
00:49:22,600 --> 00:49:26,430
Take it easy!
lt'll all happen in time.

464
00:49:27,770 --> 00:49:30,150
This is the job.

465
00:49:30,350 --> 00:49:34,020
Don't wait for it to happen,
don't even want it to happen.

466
00:49:34,230 --> 00:49:36,860
Just watch what does happen.

467
00:49:38,070 --> 00:49:40,110
Are you my 'tutor'?

468
00:49:41,320 --> 00:49:44,160
Yes, sir, that I am.

469
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:49,830
- Did you check it already?
- Yes, I did.

470
00:49:50,040 --> 00:49:52,130
Then leave it alone.

471
00:49:52,790 --> 00:49:55,380
You're a good cop, Giuseppe.

472
00:49:55,590 --> 00:49:59,220
You're doing good.
You're gonna do just fine.

