- You heard me, Capone. It's over.

952
01:51:27,570 --> 01:51:30,120
You're nothin'
but a lot of talk and a badge.

953
01:51:30,320 --> 01:51:33,120
Here endeth the lesson.

954
01:51:33,330 --> 01:51:37,580
You're nothin'
but a lot of talk and a badge!

955
01:51:37,790 --> 01:51:41,000
You're nothin'
but a lot of talk and a badge!

956
01:52:59,120 --> 01:53:01,290
So much violence.

957
01:54:07,480 --> 01:54:09,900
Cleaning up a little.

958
01:54:18,580 --> 01:54:21,580
I guess this is goodbye.

959
01:54:22,910 --> 01:54:24,500
Goodbye, George.

960
01:54:27,130 --> 01:54:30,210
I want to...thank you for this.

961
01:54:31,300 --> 01:54:33,090
No. Thank you.

962
01:54:48,980 --> 01:54:53,610
Mr Ness... I think he would have
wanted you to have that.

963
01:54:53,820 --> 01:54:56,910
He'd have wanted a cop to have it.

964
01:55:00,530 --> 01:55:03,120
I'm going home.

965
01:55:14,050 --> 01:55:16,680
Mr Ness!
Any comment for the record?

966
01:55:16,880 --> 01:55:19,590
'The man who put
Al Capone on the spot.'

967
01:55:19,760 --> 01:55:22,350
I just happened to be there
when the wheel went round.

968
01:55:22,560 --> 01:55:25,560
They say they're going
to repeal prohibition.

969
01:55:25,770 --> 01:55:28,850
- What will you do then?
- I think I'll have a drink.